# 11. Improve Chunking Strategy

This is probably one of the biggest technical gains available.

Most Islamic texts are hierarchical:

```text
كتاب
  باب
    فصل
      مسألة
```

Current chunking probably cuts across semantic boundaries.

Instead:

## Hierarchical chunking

Store:

```json
{
  "kitab": "",
  "bab": "",
  "fasl": "",
  "masala": ""
}
```

Then retrieval can rank:

* same mas’ala
* same bab
* same kitab

This improves relevance enormously.

